source: This mission requires teammates and does not work as a mercenary.
target: 该任务需要队友，不能只有佣兵。
守卫可能获得的奖励只有

source: Creates a buy zone where you're standing. Chemicals in this buy zone will be discounted.
target: 在你的位置创建一个购买区，里面的化学品会打折。

source: Used to capture Conquest control points. Place this directly onto a control point to capture it.
target: 用来立刻占领征服模式中的控制点。直接将它放置在控制点上即可占领。

source: Creates a supply drop at your current location.
target: 在你当前位置呼叫一批空降补给。

source: Teleports you to other Warp Fields (you need at least 2). Stand in it, hold ALT, and click an arrow to teleport.
target: 横跨地图的远程传送。站在扭曲立场范围里，按住ALT键，依照箭头指示，选择传送到达的扭曲力场、基地或控制点。

source: Reveals enemies within {{%01%}} meters of it.

target: 提升你的武器额外伤害

source: Allows you to capture enemy chemicals by standing on top of them.
target: 能让你站在敌方化学品上来占领它

source: Protects your chemicals from enemy Neutralizers. Place this on a chemical and if an enemy tries to neutralize it, it will remove the Insulator but save the original chemical. Can only be used once per chemical.
target: 保护你的药剂避免陷入敌手。把这个绝缘体放置在药剂上，当敌方试图破坏时，绝缘体将消失，但药剂本身可保留下来，仅限一次性使用。

source: Reveals the location of nearby enemy chemicals making them easier to neutralize. The revealing range is
target: 显示周围敌人的化学物来让他们更好中和，显示距离是

source: Upgrade: Makes the chemical you're standing in invisible to enemies unless they stand inside it.
target: 升级：让你站在里面的化学品永久对敌人隐蔽。

source: Enemies in your Goo Trap are slowed for {{%01%}} seconds.
Creates a laser that zaps enemies who walk through it. This deals {{%01%}} of their current health.
target: 制造激光来对经过的敌人造成伤害，这将会造成{{%01%}}的当前生命值

source: Explodes for {{%01%}} hp damage when an enemy steps inside it.
target: 敌人踩在里面过后爆炸造成 {{%01%}}生命值伤害。

source: Extends your magazine by giving a free bullet every {{%01%}} shots.
target: 每{{%01%}}射击后给予一发免费子弹。

source: Your bullets slow civs and cops by {{%01%}} for {{%02%}}.
target: 你的子弹会减速平民与警察 {{%01%}} ， {{%02%}}秒

source: Your gun's critical damage will increase by {{%01%}} when you kill an enemy player or a cop. This can go {{%02%}} higher than the default cap of {{%03%}}.
target: 当你击杀一名敌方玩家或警察时，你的武器的暴击伤害提高 {{%01%}}。这将比默认上限 {{%03%}}.高出{{%02%}} 。
每{{%01%}} 秒给予免费手雷

source: This is placed into the map and is hidden from enemies unless they stand inside it.
target: 安置在地图中，敌方直到站在里面时都不可见，

source: Does not work as a zombie.

target: 级还有，即可获取协同点数

source: You will gain {{%01%}} health per second for every point in the Physical tree.
target: 每一点消耗在体能技能树的点会提供 {{%01%}} 生命值每秒。

source: You will regenerate shifts {{%01%}}% faster for every point in the Mental tree.
target: 每一点消耗在灵能技能树的点会提供 {{%01%}}% 闪现充能速率。

source: You will deal {{%01%}}% more bullet damage for every point in the Cybernetic tree.
target: 每一点消耗在赛博改造技能树的点会提供 {{%01%}} %更高的子弹伤害。

source: You can take a skill up to level 3 once you've spent {{%01%}} points in its skill tree.
target: 只要你花费{{%01%}}点至其技能树，你就能获取最高等级至3的技能。

source: Whenever you kill an enemy they'll leave a puddle of blood on the ground that damages other enemies who step in it.
target: 当你击杀敌人时候会留下一滩血来对上方的敌人造成伤害。

source: Increases the cash and health you gain from killing enemy players and cops. This increases further based on your wanted level. By default, player kills give +{{%01%}} health.
target: 提高你从击杀敌方玩家和警察时获取的现金与生命值，该加成基于你的通缉等级，默认玩家击杀给予+{{%01%}}生命值。

source: Allows you to shoot out the window of your car while driving (with worse accuracy). Also increases your top boosting speed.
Makes you jump higher when standing in your chemicals. Also makes your chemicals restore charges faster. Also puts chemicals on discount from vendors.
Spawns grenades that spin around you. These grenades will be randomly tossed at nearby enemies over time.
Whenever you fall onto the ground near an enemy you will reduce their rate of fire. Enemies killed in this state will drop a heart piece on death.
target: 当你落在敌人附近时，你会减少他的射击速率，当敌人在这个状态下被击杀会掉落一个心之碎片。

source: Restores health by a percentage of the damage you deal to enemies.
target: 根据你造成伤害的百分比恢复生命值。

source: Makes you heal faster when out of combat. By default players heal at {{%01%}} hp/s after {{%02%}}s.
target: 当你脱离战斗时恢复更快，默认时玩家在脱战 {{%02%}}秒后以 {{%01%}}生命值每秒恢复。
治疗你自己和周围友军。

source: Creates a shield that blocks enemy bullets.
target: 制造一个护盾来挡住敌方子弹。

source: Makes you invisible as long as you don't stand too close to an enemy player or cop.
target: 让你在远离敌方玩家或警察时隐身。

source: Slows the speed of all bullets in a circle around you. Any bullets you fire within Bullet Time will steer towards enemies.
target: 减少你周围所有的子弹飞行速度，你在子弹时间内射击的子弹会加速冲向敌军。

source: Increases your rate of fire. This also applies to nearby allies when you cast it.
target: 当激活时提高你的射速，同时也提高你周围友军的射速。

source: Creates deadly blades that spin around you and slash nearby enemies. After a short time these blades will bursts out to deal damage at range.
target: 制造致命的刀刃在你周围旋转并伤害敌人，短时间过后这些刀刃会爆炸并造成伤害。

source: Shocks all enemy players and bullets in front of you. Shocking an enemy will make their bullets travel slower. Also, bullets hit by your Shockwave will be frozen in mid-air.
target: 震撼你前方所有的敌人和子弹，被震撼的敌人子弹会飞的更慢，冲击波命中的子弹会在半空中静止。

source: Launches a long range nuke that creates a large radioactive field. Enemies that step into this take damage over time, and take additional damage if hit by the initial blast.
target: 发射一个远距离的核弹，造成大范围的辐射区，在区域内的敌人会受到持续伤害，如果被直接炸到会受到额外伤害。

source: Fires a poison dart that deals damage over time. This damage can't kill enemy players, but can reduce them to 1hp.
target: 发射一枚毒镖造成持续伤害，此伤害无法击杀敌人但会削减至生命值1。

source: Launches an explosive ball of plasma that gains damage the further it travels.
target: 发射一个等离子爆炸球，伤害根据飞行距离提高。

source: Creates a shield around you whenever you cast a skill. This will briefly protect you from enemy weapon damage.
target: 每次发动技能时保护自己免受敌方武器伤害。

source: Your bullets will briefly deal extra damage after shifting. This does not apply when you shift without charges and lose health.
target: 你的子弹会在漂移后造成额外伤害，当你没有漂移充能时不生效。

source: Makes you move faster by drifting on air. Your weapons also have no movement slowdown while drifting. Cast again to stop drifting.
Bounces bullets off your Force Field. Also causes your Force Field to deal damage to nearby enemies when it explodes.
target: 你的力场会弹开子弹，并且当力场爆炸时对周围敌人造成伤害。

source: Creates a spinning vortex on the ground that slows enemies. You will steal health from each enemy caught inside it.
target: 制造一个旋转的涡流对敌人减速，你将会从每一个在涡流内部的敌人偷取生命值

source: Increases your bullet speed and range.
Improves the speed that you can reload and swap between weapons.
target: 提高重装弹药及武器切换速度。

source: Lets you see through walls by revealing nearby enemies and loot crates. Also briefly reveals enemies after you damage them.
target: 能让你穿墙看见敌人和战利品箱子，并暂时透视你对其造成伤害的敌人。

source: Makes your bullets bounce off walls.
target: 让你的子弹可以从墙上反弹。

source: Slows the movement speed of all enemies within your radiation field.
target: 自身辐射场范围内，敌方移动速度变慢。

source: Throws a line of spikes onto the ground that damage enemies who walk across it.
target: 往地上丢一条尖刺来伤害穿过的敌人。

source: Fires additional balls when you cast Plasma Ball. These extra balls do reduced damage.

Whenever you are damaged by an enemy, Counter Spell will automatically trigger and reduce that incoming damage. It provides extra strong protection against non-bullet damage. After triggering it must recharge.
target: 当你被敌人造成伤害时候，反击法术会自动触发并减少伤害，他会对非子弹伤害额外提供保护，当触发后必须重新充能。

source: Throws a smoke bomb on the ground that instantly makes you invisible. You will remain invisible as long as you stay inside the smoke.
target: 投掷一个瞬间爆炸的烟雾弹来让你隐身，你将持续在烟雾里隐身，

source: Steals enemy bullets and seeks them back towards your enemies. This occurs when you toggle off Bullet Time.
target: 将你的子弹发射回你的敌人哪，当你关闭子弹时间时起效。

source: When Frenzy is active, each bullet you fire has a chance to not reduce your ammo, extending your magazine size.
target: 当狂怒启用时，你的子弹都有一定机会不消耗子弹，扩大你的弹匣容量。

source: Marks your position with an X on the ground. After a short time (or when you cast again) you'll teleport back to this location and restore lost health.
target: 在你的位置标记一个X，当短时间后(或再次释放技能)你会传送回这个地方并且恢复失去的生命值。

source: Speeds up your skill cooldowns whenever you get a kill. The reduction is a percentage of the remaining cooldown time.
You'll gain health based on a percentage of the damage you deal with parasites.
target: 你将会根据寄生虫造成的伤害百分比恢复生命值。

source: Infected enemies will take increased weapon damage. They will also leave a trail on the ground that infects other enemies, applying Venom to them as well.
target: 被感染的敌人会受到额外的武器伤害。同时感染者会在地上留下痕迹可进一步感染其他敌人。

source: Summons an orb that increases the damage of your bullets when they fly through it. Does not work when you stand within it.
target: 召唤一个光球，子弹穿过光球造成额外伤害，如你站在光球内则不生效。

source: Fires a stream of parasites that bounce off walls and penetrate through enemies. Briefly disables your weapons.
target: 发射一串寄生虫从墙上弹走并穿透敌人，暂时禁用你的武器。

source: Creates a clone of you that confuses enemies. This clone will move towards your target. It will shoot, but not do any damage.
target: 制造你的克隆来迷惑敌人，这个克隆会移动并假装射击，但无法造成伤害。

source: Increases the damage of all your skills. Also whenever you cast a skill, the next bullet you shoot with be enchanted with extra damage.
target: 提高你所有技能造成的伤害，当你释放技能时，你下一发子弹会被强化并造成额外伤害。

source: Pretty awful as a car. But it's cheap and makes a nice step for jumping over walls.
target: 作为车来说太烂了，好在便宜，就用来跳过墙壁吧。

source: Fast and agile - just watch out for the low health. If it catches on fire you'll burn.
target: 一辆快捷的车 - 但要注意那点血量，它要是着火你也会跟着一起着火。

source: Fast and durable - a great all-rounder. Can survive a direct shot from a Bazooka.
target: 又快又结实的载具，总体都不错，甚至能正面硬抗一发火箭筒！

source: A good combat vehicle great for co-op drivebys. Press [F3] to hop into the back and shoot.
target: 不错的战斗载具，尤其适合装载友军协作战斗。按[F3]键可跳到背后进行360度的射击。

source: Has a radar that sees through walls and reveals the location of nearby enemies.
target: 此载具带有雷达，可发现附近敌人。拿它来当穿墙眼，透视敌人的行动吧！

source: Very durable for its price and with 6 seats it's great for transporting your squad.
target: 就性价比而言，此载具超皮实，带6个座位尤其适合装载友军协作战斗。载客越多，载具自我恢复就越快，使得蹲点阴人者变得很难对付。

source: Fastest car in the game. Hold [SHIFT] to boost and scoop up all the loot in the map.
target: 游戏中最快的车！ 按[SHIFT]可以提升和东京漂移到处。

source: Comes with a ticking time bomb. [LEFT CLICK] to toggle the timer on and off.
target: 此载具带有定时炸弹！按[鼠标左键]切换倒计时开/关状态，它爆炸时自己一定要离远点！

source: A huge truck with massive health and 5 passenger seats. The back 3 seats allow for drivebys.
target: 血条超长的大型卡车，带5个座位，其中3个后座可进行360度无死角射击。售价昂贵，但与友军乘此载具协同作战，势不可挡。

source: Fires 2 homing missiles that deal extra damage against vehicles. [LEFT CLICK] to fire.
target: 按[鼠标左键]发射2枚跟踪导弹，可对敌载具和丧尸造成巨大伤害。售价昂贵，但使用得法，必成致命大杀器。·

source: Drive the Extraction Truck to its extraction zone.
target: 把撤离卡车开到撤离点。

source: [LEFT CLICK] to fire a smoking hot Flamethrower. The Cybertruck's windows are shatterproof.
target: [鼠标左键]来发射一个致命火焰，这个赛博卡车是防爆的。

source: [LEFT CLICK] to turn on the siren and scare off gangsters up to no good.
target: [鼠标左键]来启用警笛并把帮派混混吓走。
爆炸物(手雷，闪光弹，燃烧瓶，巴祖卡)
手枪(USP，沙鹰，信号枪，电击枪)
狙击枪(鲁格，巴雷特，中子光束)

source: Silent and deadly. Great for finishing enemies off at close range.
target: 无声且致命，适用于在近距离击杀敌人。

source: Kaboom! Deals more damage the closer it lands to your enemies.
target: 轰隆！如果手雷在守卫附近爆炸，他们会朝声响的方向查看。

source: Explodes with a huge flash of light that blinds nearby enemies.
target: 爆炸并发出巨大闪光，几秒内致盲附近敌人。它爆炸时，要先躲好，别闪着自己。

source: Fires a homing missile that deals huge damage against vehicles.
target: 发射一发火箭弹，可对载具或丧尸群造成严重伤害。附近的守卫会朝爆炸声响的方向查看。

source: A silenced pistol with a fast switch time. Unlike other guns, you won't be revealed when firing it.
target: 精度不错的无声手枪。附近的守卫不会听见开枪的动静。

source: High damage makes this a great sidearm. Does extra damage vs civs and cops.
target: 很棒的副武器，高杀伤、高开火率，就是载弹量太低。像手枪一样，其子弹伤害输出与射程无关，一直保持满额杀伤力。

source: An extremely mobile superweapon that fires bullets that slow civs and cops.
target: 一种极度移动的超级武器，可以减缓敌人的速度。

source: A great run & gun weapon with the fastest movement speed in the game.
target: 超快的子弹火速对敌人严重伤害，可是特别不准。

source: A high rof and high movement speed make this a great all-round weapon.
target: 低后坐力，高移动力，总体评价很靠谱。

source: A high damage superweapon. Its bullets pierce through enemies.
target: 大杀器之一。其子弹可在墙上反弹并可击穿敌方掩体。

source: Does huge damage at point blank range.
target: 有限距离内可秒杀敌人，超出距离就不行了，只能击晕敌人。

source: An auto-shotgun with huge close range DPS.
target: 近距离输出惊人的自动霰弹枪。冲到敌人身边，再把他们崩飞！

source: A powerful superweapon that fires explosive bullets. Hold the fire button to charge an extra powerful blast.
target: 一个强而有力的超级武器射击爆破弹药，按住射击键来充能以射击巨大爆炸。

source: Very effective at range, but you'll need to burst fire to control its recoil.
target: 长距离特别有效，可是必须站着控制后坐力。

source: Accurate and great at range. Fires in short bursts of 3.
target: 精准的远距离武器，三连发。

source: An extremely accurate superweapon that fires seeking bullets.
target: 大杀器之一，发射准得要命的跟踪子弹。锁定敌人，发射的子弹会自动追踪他们，输出又快又狠的伤害。

source: Has a huge clip size and deals extra vehicle damage.
target: 超大弹匣，可对载具输出严重伤害。移动中命中率相当糟糕，边走边射，一无所获。

source: Fires long range bullets and deals extra vehicle damage.
target: 超大弹匣，可对载具输出严重伤害。会减慢移动速度，移动中射击还啥都打不着。

source: An extremely high damage superweapon that deals extra damage against vehicles.
target: 大杀器之一，可对载具输出严重伤害。

source: A sniper with an extended scope lets you see enemies further away.
target: 给你一个加长瞄准镜来看的更远并从屏幕外狙击他们。

source: Fires extremely fast bullets and with a scope for long range sniping.
target: 经典的狙击枪，带瞄准镜可提供额外观察范围。发射又快又准的子弹，杀伤力随飞行距离而增加。

source: A deadly superweapon that fires a beam of photons. Its bullets pierce through enemies.
target: 长距离大杀器，发射一束光子，可击穿敌方掩体或防御技能效果。作为究极狙击武器而言，有着极高的精度和杀伤力！

source: Tosses a flaming bottle that explodes on impact.
target: 投掷燃烧瓶，接触即炸，任何经过者都会被烧伤。

source: Fires a flare that explodes on impact. Good for shooting enemies behind cover.
target: 发射一个信号弹，受到撞击时爆炸，跟小火箭筒一样。

source: An extremely deadly superweapon that shoots fire and sets cars on fire.
target: 大杀器之一，喷火点燃击中的一切物体，造成持续烧伤，对丧尸群威力惊人。

source: Aww man, you got blood on my shirt.
target: 老铁啊，血都溅我身上了。

source: Nearby allies support you by slowly regenerating your mana and health.
target: 邻近友军正在缓慢回复你的HP和灵能。
鼠标停在这里可查看技能菜单。

source: Left click skills to add them. Right click to view them.
target: 鼠标左键点击技能来添加，右键点击来预览。

source: Click 'Start Adding Skills' to create a skill build.
target: 点击“开始添加技能点”创建技能组。

source: If you die you become a zombie. But you can revive by killing a survivor. Or you can collect 4 heart pieces by winning a heart supply drop.
target: 如果你死了你将变成僵尸，但是你能通过击杀一个幸存者(红色)或赢取心之容器。

source: Press ({{%01%}}) to chat. Say 'wassup' to receive a bonus 10xp!
Welcome mutant! To win you'll need to get stronger. The best way to level up is to kill enemies (wearing red).
target: 欢迎突变者！想胜利，你必须变得更强大。击杀敌人来获取现金及经验。

source: Buy a grenade and then blow up a civilian. Throw nades with middle mouse or ({{%01%}}).
target: 手雷是非常好用的，购买一些并且拿来炸死平民，用鼠标滚轮或({{%01%}})投掷手雷。

source: Enter a car with ({{%01%}}), then kill a cop. You can shoot out the window when your car isn't moving.
target: 按 ({{%01%}}) 进入汽车,然后击杀警察，当车停止时可以向窗外射击。

source: Hold ({{%01%}}) and click 'Reset Skill Build' from the drop-down skills menu up the top of the screen.
target: 按住 ({{%01%}})并从下落技能目录中点击

source: Leveling up gives you skill points. Hold ({{%01%}}) and spend a skill point on SELF REPAIR.
Active skills are shown above your health bar. Press ({{%01%}}) to cast Self Repair. This can be cast every 15s.
This is the Outbreak game mode. To win you need to kill zombies, collect their souls and return them to the bomb.
target: 这里是大爆发游戏模式。想赢得游戏，需要击杀丧尸，收集掉落的尸魂，再回填到炸弹里并引爆。尽量使用范围杀伤，要比仅用枪射击有效得多。

source: After collecting souls you need to return them to the bomb. Follow the arrow on your screen to take your souls to the bomb. Hold (TAB) to see scores.
target: 收集尸魂后，需要回填到炸弹里，每次回填都有分数、金钱、灵能、生命值和经验奖励。按HUD上显示的白色箭头行动，把尸魂填入炸弹。按住(TAB)键可查看分数。

source: Under the minimap you'll see a 'Kill Contract'. This increases over time and is awarded to you on your next kill.
target: 小地图下你能看见“击杀合同”，这个会根据时间变多并在你获得下一次击杀时给予。

source: Use a car ({{%01%}}) to escape the blue circle in the minimap. Or pay your bounty at a vendor.
Try different vendors until you see the FISSION MINE chemical, then buy it. When carrying this you'll passively get free grenades.
target: 试试去其他商人哪购买分裂地雷化学品，当携带时你会被动获取免费手雷。

source: Place your 'Fission Mine' in a busy area by holding ({{%01%}}). This makes a hidden bomb that will detonate when enemies step in it.
Stand inside your shop and buy something. You can place shops as long as you have charges.
target: 站在你的商店里购买一些东西，你只要有充能就你放置商店。

source: Pick up your chemical by standing in it and pressing ({{%01%}}).
target: 站在你的化学品并按下({{%01%}})来拾取。

source: In Conquest you need to capture all of the Control Points in the map.
target: 这是占领模式，你需要占领地图上所有的据点。你可以配合“占领者”化学药剂加速占领。在出生点购买“占领者”化学药剂。

source: Capture a point by standing next to it. The more allies nearby, the faster you will capture.
target: 站在占领点附近来占领它，周围的队友更多，占领速度越快。

source: This is the Extraction game mode. Follow the white arrow on your screen to capture the enemy flag.
target: 这里是提取游戏模式。想赢得游戏，需要占领目标（像是旗帜、电台或卡车），并带回对应的提取区域。按HUD上白色箭头指示行动，占领当前目标。

source: Follow the arrow and take the flag to the enemy flag near your spawn. Hold (TAB) to see scores.
target: 一旦占领了目标，就必须提取它。按HUD上白色箭头指示行动，到达对应提取区域。成功提取目标，可奖励己方全员大量分数，所以好好配合吧！按住(TAB)键来查看分数。

source: This is the Checkpoint game mode. To win you need do laps with the Battery in a vehicle. Grab a car, then follow the white arrow on your screen to pick up the Battery.
target: 这里是剧情点游戏模式。想赢得游戏，需要捡起电池，放进载具，完成通过全部剧情点的跑圈。购买载具，按HUD上白色箭头指示行动，占领电池。

source: Follow the white arrow on your screen to drive the battery through each of the checkpoints. Hold (TAB) to see scores.
target: 载着电池，完成通过全部剧情点的跑圈。按HUD上白色箭头指示行动，通过全部重生点。如果是敌方载着电池，你可以在设置路障妨害他们跑圈。按住(TAB)键来查看分数。

source: Stand inside an enemy chemical, hold ({{%01%}}), and select 'Neutralize Chemicals' to destroy it.
target: 站在敌军化学品，并按住({{%01%}})，选择“中和化学品”来摧毁它。

source: Press (F10) to finish this tutorial. This opens the How to Play Guide if you want to learn more.
target: 你通过了新人练习，按(F10)来结束训练。如果你想要知道更多这会打开玩法指南。

source: Win round one to get bonus XP and cash. The player count is shown above the minimap.
target: 赢得第一回合来获取额外经验与现金，玩家数量在小地图上方显示。

source: Search for a civilian with yellow text above him. Then hold ({{%01%}}) and buy an MP5 (a tier 2 gun).
target: 寻找一个头顶上有黄色字符的平民，按住({{%01%}})以购买MP5 (2阶武器)。

source: Right Click ({{%01%}}) to shift. Be careful - you'll take damage if you shift without charges (the little white triangles).
Shifts briefly increase your damage (shown in purple). Kill a civilian with critical bullets by shifting just before you shoot.
target: 漂移暂时的提高你造成的伤害(紫色)，漂移后立即开火来使用暴击子弹击杀平民。

source: A full game has 3 rounds, but you only need to win the FINAL round. Use earlier rounds to level up and prepare for the final showdown!
target: 一局完整游戏有4个回合，但是你只需要赢得最后回合，在早期回合中升级并准备最终试炼。

source: XP is now enabled. Get kills until you level up. Your level is shown next to the health bar.
target: 经验值现在已启用，获得击杀直到你升级，你的等级在生命条附近显示。

source: To win you need to level up. Missions help you do this faster. Follow the mission arrow on your screen then press ({{%01%}}).
target: 找到一个有绿色文本气泡的市民并按下({{%01%}})。

source: Missions are shown above the minimap. For this mission you'll earn cash and XP if you kill 4 cops.
target: 任务在小地图上方显示，做任务来让你比你的敌人升级更快！这个任务需要你击杀6名警察。

source: Learn to play and earn bonus XP!
target: 试着按新手指南操作吧！顺序完成每个步骤，都有经验值奖励！

source: The player count, timer, and your score are shown here.
target: 玩家数量，计时器还有你的分数在这里显示。

source: Your health, lives and shifts are shown down here.
target: 你的生命值，灵能还有闪现次数在这下面显示。

source: Press Q to switch weapons, and middle mouse to throw grenades.
target: 按Q切换武器，按鼠标滚轮投掷手雷。

source: Press 1, 2, 3 to cast skills. Hold ALT to spend skill points.
target: 按1，2，3释放技能，按住ALT来使用技能点。

source: to toggle this guide on and off.

The meaning of life, the universe and everything you need to know about Gene Shift Auto can be found in this guide; so toggle this back on when you're ready to play like a pro. Until then you can press ENTER to chat with the server and ask questions. Have fun!
target: 本指南可为您解读游戏的全部信息！游戏老手可切换指南信息为关闭状态。按回车键，可与服务器交谈或提问。祝游戏愉快！

source: I JUST WANT TO STOP DYING!!

target: 了解你的武器，新兵蛋子！
没时间解释了，快发车吧？

source: EARN A LITTLE EXTRA ON THE SIDE..
What do I have to do?
Follow the arrow on your screen to reach the next checkpoint. Try to earn combo kills to gain extra cash.
target: 按屏幕箭头指示，到达下一个剧情点。试着打出连杀，可获得额外金钱奖励。消灭丧尸，收集尸魂并填充到炸弹里，就能引爆了。

source: What if I miss some text?
target: 我漏掉了一些信息提示怎么办？

source: Press (ENTER) to bring up the chat log. The green lines have important tips. Also when playing singleplayer you can hold (ALT) to pause the game and read the text at your own pace.
target: 按回车键打开聊天记录，绿字信息都是重要提示。单人游戏时，也可按住(ALT)键暂停游戏，慢慢阅读提示信息。

source: Stay out of combat for a few seconds to trigger auto-heal. Use vehicles for protection while looting. Unlock healing skills with (ALT). Buy expensive weapons to deal extra damage.
target: 暂时离开战斗来治疗你自己。站在圆形的检查点内即可按下(B)键购买武器。最后，按下(ALT)键来解锁治愈技能，并使用右键、C键和F键来使用这些技能。

source: To win, simply be the last man standing on the final round. The best way to do this is to earn cash and XP in the earlier rounds to become as strong as possible.
target: 想胜利，只需要在最后回合活到最后。最好的方式是在早期回合中获得现金和经验来发育自己。

source: Kill civilians and players to earn cash and XP. Unlock healing skills and buy a tier 2 gun as soon as possible. If you become a zombie, head towards a heart crate to try revive.
target: 避免死亡圈，并试着活着。 如果你成为一个僵尸，利用这段时间抢劫现金，技能和化学品。 使用Warp Fields快速传送到中心购买区。

source: When you view the skills page through the main menu you're looking at your permanent skill build. This build is only used in permanent multiplayer servers and persists between rounds. This build is not used in quickmatches or the campaign.
target: 通过主菜单浏览到技能页面，现在看到的是你的永久技能组合。此组合只可用于永久多人服务器，比赛中不可更改。此组合不可用于快速比赛或战役模式。

source: DLC owners can host their own legacy game modes and play against bots. To play against humans it's better to join an official server.
target: 你或许不想看见这些信息。想玩多人游戏，请加入官方服务器！想与朋友们一起玩战役模式，请点击战役模式页面，再加入游戏即可。

source: Customize your skill draft with the buttons down the bottom right.
target: 左下角的按键以编辑你的技能池。

source: TIP: Try enabling skills that work well together and disable the rest. EG: Create a 'Sniper' build with long ranged skills only, like Energize and Plasma Ball. This way you only see relevant skills in-game.
target: 小提示：尝试启用能配合使用的技能并禁用其他的，比如:制造一个

source: Free accounts can only save {{%01%}} builds at a time. Delete an existing build, or get the DLC to create as many builds as you want!
target: 基本账户只能保存 {{%01%}} 构筑，删除一个现有构筑或获取DLC来建立无限的构筑。

source: You can improve your FPS by updating your graphics drivers. For now, would you like Gene Shift Auto to optimise your graphics settings?
target: 你的FPS低于60，你可以升级显卡驱动、或者降低游戏画质来提升FPS，尝试解决此问题？
正在获取更新信息，从版本

source: requires a manual download. Get Gene Shift Auto for free on Steam now!
target: 须手动到 www.geneshiftauto.com 下载！

source: Couldn't connect to GSN (Gene Shift Auto Network).
target: 无法连接到GSN (Gene Shift Auto Network)。

source: NEW VERSION: Click here to download

target: 有新版本：正在获取更新信息

source: NEW VERSION REQUIRES MANUAL DOWNLOAD: Download
target: 须手动下载新版本：下载完成
即将完成：更新将在重启游戏后生效

source: NEW VERSION RELEASED: Please restart Steam to force an update.
target: 新版本已发布：请重启steam安装更新。

source: THE REST OF THIS FILE IS FROM THE SINGLEPLAYER CAMPAIGN.
target: 此文件的其余部分来自单人游戏战役。
